asefire Stills Holds Amid New Attacks</media:title><media:player url="https://www.today.com/video/us-and-iran-exchange-fire-as-trump-insists-ceasefire-is-holding-262976069706"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778238871989_tdy_news_7a_bradley_welker_trump_iran_260508_S3_1920x1080-07uqxw.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">President Donald Trump says the fragile ceasefire is still in effect even as attacks escalate between the United States and Iran in the Strait of Hormuz. U.S. Central Command said Iran fired missiles and launched drones at three American destroyers, calling the attacks “unprovoked.” They also said U.S. forces responded with self defense strikes targeting military facilities and drone launch sites in Iran. Iran says it was the U.S. who fired first and that its attacks were defensive. NBC’s Matt Bradley reports and Kristen Welker, moderator of Meet the Press, joins TODAY with analysis.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778238871989_tdy_news_7a_bradley_welker_trump_iran_260508.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778238871989_tdy_news_7a_bradley_welker_trump_iran_260508.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778238871989_tdy_news_7a_bradley_welker_trump_iran_260508_S3_1920x1080-07uqxw.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 11:14:39 GMT</pubDate><title>Trump Says US and Iran Ceasefire Stills Holds Amid New Attacks</title><updateDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 11:15:44 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Michael Kosnar</dc:creator><dc:creator>Steve Kopack</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Thu, 07 May 2026 21:56:36 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The Justice Department and the CFTC are probing a series of highly profitable oil market trades made just ahead of major policy announcements on the Iran war.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/energy/doj-probes-oil-prediction-markets-iran-news-rcna344135</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/energy/doj-probes-oil-prediction-markets-iran-news-rcna344135</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260507-oil-barrels-ch-1648-93ce72.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Brandon Bell</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Refinery.</media:text><media:description type="plain">An aerial view of smoke from a refinery on June 14, 2024 in Houston.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260507-oil-barrels-ch-1648-93ce72.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 21:56:36 GMT</pubDate><title>DOJ probing trades in oil futures and prediction markets just ahead of major Iran war news</title><updateDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 23:33:16 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Alexander Smith</dc:creator><dc:contributor>The Associated Press</dc:contributor><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 08 May 2026 07:38:32 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Early results Friday from nationwide elections in Britain suggested a historic drubbing for Prime Minister Keir Starmer’s Labour Party and sweeping gains for hard-right Reform U.K., led by Trump ally Nigel Farage.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/united-kingdom/starmer-labour-reform-farage-uk-election-rcna344013</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/united-kingdom/starmer-labour-reform-farage-uk-election-rcna344013</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260508-starmer-rs-6e118f.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Justin Tallis</media:credit><media:text type="plain">TOPSHOT-BRITAIN-POLITICS-VOTE</media:text><media:description type="plain">Britain&#39;s Prime Minister Keir Starmer (L) arrives with his wife Victoria Starmer (R) to cast their votes at a polling station in Westminster Chapel, central London on May 7, 2026, as polls open for local elections. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260508-farage-rs-fc7b1a.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Chris Radburn</media:credit><media:text type="plain">TOPSHOT-BRITAIN-POLITICS-VOTE</media:text><media:description type="plain">Farage outside a polling station in Walton-on-the-Naze, eastern England on Thursday. His anti-establishment, anti-immigration message appears to have broken through.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260508-green-rs-ce16a9.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1666" width="2500"><media:credit>Jon Rowley</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Wales Green Party Leader Anthony Slaughter Votes In The 2026 Senedd Election</media:text><media:description type="plain">Green Party leader Zack Polanski has been popular with voters.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260508-starmer-rs-6e118f.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 07:38:32 GMT</pubDate><title>Hard-right party routs Starmer’s Labour in U.K. elections as Trump ally hails ‘historic shift’</title><updateDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 08:52:19 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Ben Kamisar</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 08 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Facing a tough election challenge is a cost of doing business for members of Congress.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/redistricting-pits-california-republican-incumbents-fight-survival-rcna343938</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/redistricting-pits-california-republican-incumbents-fight-survival-rcna343938</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260506-Ken-Calvert-Young-Kim-ch-1644-f794d8.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="800" width="1200"><media:credit>Getty Images</media:credit><media:text type="plain">A split composite of Young Kim and Ken Calvert.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Young Kim; Ken Calvert.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260506-Ken-Calvert-Young-Kim-ch-1644-f794d8.jpg" height="800" width="1200"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate><title>Redistricting pits California Republican incumbents against each other in a fight for survival</title><updateDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 08 May 2026 11:12:16 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The ship at the center of the deadly hantavirus outbreak is heading to the Canary Islands as health officials scramble to track passengers who disembarked from the ship early. It comes as new suspected cases are popping in multiple countries, including in the United Kingdom and Singapore. NBC’s Daniele Hamamdjian reports for TODAY from Tenerife.</description><expires>2056-05-08T11:11:34.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">tdy_news_7a_hamamdjian_hantavirus_spread_260508</guid><link>https://www.today.com/video/new-suspected-hantavirus-cases-pop-up-in-multiple-countries-262975045824</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/tdy_news_7a_hamamdjian_hantavirus_spread_260508/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Officials Race to Track Hantavirus After Outbreak on Cruise Ship</media:title><media:player url="https://www.today.com/video/new-suspected-hantavirus-cases-pop-up-in-multiple-countries-262975045824"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778238678511_tdy_news_7a_hamamdjian_hantavirus_spread_260508_S3_1920x1080-02hm75.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">The ship at the center of the deadly hantavirus outbreak is heading to the Canary Islands as health officials scramble to track passengers who disembarked from the ship early. It comes as new suspected cases are popping in multiple countries, including in the United Kingdom and Singapore. NBC’s Daniele Hamamdjian reports for TODAY from Tenerife.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778238678511_tdy_news_7a_hamamdjian_hantavirus_spread_260508.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778238678511_tdy_news_7a_hamamdjian_hantavirus_spread_260508.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778238678511_tdy_news_7a_hamamdjian_hantavirus_spread_260508_S3_1920x1080-02hm75.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 11:11:25 GMT</pubDate><title>Officials Race to Track Hantavirus After Outbreak on Cruise Ship</title><updateDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 11:12:16 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Suzanne Gamboa</dc:creator><dc:creator>Mike Hixenbaugh</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Thu, 07 May 2026 18:34:20 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Daniel Savala, who preached for decades in an Assemblies of God-run college ministry, was sentenced to 30 years in prison without the possibility of parole.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/daniel-savala-christian-missionary-pleads-guilty-abusing-boys-rcna343859</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/daniel-savala-christian-missionary-pleads-guilty-abusing-boys-rcna343859</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2025-07/250729-daniel-savala-group-cs-7e5e14.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1158" width="1606"><media:credit>Courtesy Olivia Wolf</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Savala poses with Eli Stewart and other young followers in Alaska in 2002.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Savala poses with Eli Stewart and other young followers in Alaska in 2002.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260507-savala-sentencing-joseph-cleveland-mn-1346-7b99d9.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1200" width="1800"><media:credit>Ilana Panich-Linsman for NBC News</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Joseph Cleveland stands outside the courthouse before delivering his victim impact statement.</media:text><media:description type="plain">&#34;You thought yourself invincible,&#34; Joseph Cleveland told Daniel Savala while giving an impact statement in court Thursday.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2025-07/250722-joseph-cleveland-houston-house-mn-1300-7b81ba.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1363" width="2743"><media:credit>Courtesy Joseph Cleveland; Google Maps</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Joseph Cleveland as a young man; Daniel Savala&#39;s house in 2018.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Joseph Cleveland as a teen; Daniel Savala&#39;s house in 2018.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260507-savala-sentencing-ron-Bloomingkemper-mn-1346-0ddb4b.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1800" width="1440"><media:credit>Ilana Panich-Linsman for NBC News</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Ron Bloomingkemper</media:text><media:description type="plain">Ron Bloomingkemper Jr., a former Chi Alpha member who for years raised alarm about Savala&#39;s actions, attended his plea hearing.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260507-savala-sentencing-joseph-cleveland-mn-1345-a2d6e5.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1200" width="1800"><media:credit>Ilana Panich-Linsman for NBC News</media:credit><media:text type="plain">From left, Krys Scroggins, Joseph Cleveland, Danny Clark, and far right, Ron Bloomingkemper, listen as Daniel Savala is sentenced.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Former Chi Alpha members, including Joseph Cleveland and Ron Bloomingkemper, listen as Daniel Savala is sentenced. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260507-savala-sentencing-joseph-cleveland-mn-1350-357541.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1025" width="1370"><media:credit>Ilana Panich-Linsman for NBC News</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Joseph Cleveland is embraced after the hearing where he gave an impact statement.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Joseph Cleveland hugs a victim support specialist from the prosecutor&#39;s office after Savala&#39;s guilty plea.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2025-07/250729-daniel-savala-group-cs-7e5e14.jpg" height="1158" width="1606"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 18:34:20 GMT</pubDate><title>Christian missionary hailed as ‘holiest man alive’ pleads guilty to abusing boys in Texas</title><updateDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 19:57:00 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Thu, 07 May 2026 17:51:16 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Blue dot fever is a term coined by the internet and tabloid newspapers for when concerts are canceled due to low ticket sales. Artists like Post Malone, Meghan Trainor and the Pussycat Dolls are just some to pull the plug on live performances over prices. </description><expires>2056-05-07T17:50:28.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">now_topstory_bluedot_fever_260507</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/video/is-blue-dot-fever-the-cause-of-tour-cancellations-262925381614</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/now_topstory_bluedot_fever_260507/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Is blue dot fever the cause of tour cancellations?</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/video/is-blue-dot-fever-the-cause-of-tour-cancellations-262925381614"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778176216346_now_topstory_bluedot_fever_260507_S3_1920x1080-9nz42i.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">Blue dot fever is a term coined by the internet and tabloid newspapers for when concerts are canceled due to low ticket sales. Artists like Post Malone, Meghan Trainor and the Pussycat Dolls are just some to pull the plug on live performances over prices. </media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778176216346_now_topstory_bluedot_fever_260507.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC